    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1866-01-30T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1866-01-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="418"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d418">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Hale</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 18.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>. <hi
                                rend="italic">Madrid,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-01-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 30, 1866.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The rebellion or insurrection of which you have
                    undoubtedly been advised, and concerning which I have already addressed to you
                    two communications, I think may now be considered as entirely suppressed.
                    General Prim, the reported leader, has made his way into Portugal. The
                    government forces sent in pursuit of the rebels have returned, and there at
                    present does not exist in Spain any organized armed opposition to the
                    government, though the proclamation placing Madrid Under martial law has not yet
                    been revoked, but continues in full force.</p>
                <p>With much respect, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>JOHN P. HALE.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary
                            of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington, D. C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
